()CertificationPhase kya hota hai?
👉 CertificationPhase = Certification ka ek stage / step
Matlab:-
Certification process ek hi baar me nahi hota, wo multiple phases me chalta hai.

🔹 CertificationPhase kya karta hai?
👉 Ye control karta hai:-
Certification abhi kis stage me hai
Next kya action hona chahiye
Reviewer kya kar sakta hai ya nahi.

🔸 Example:-
👉 Agar phase = Active
Reviewer approve/revoke kar sakta hai ✅
👉 Agar phase = Completed
Kuch change nahi kar sakta ❌

🔹 Kya DB me store hota hai?
👉 ❌ Direct “CertificationPhase” naam ka alag object/table usually nahi hota
👉 ✅ Lekin:-
Phase ki value Certification object ke andar store hoti hai
🔸 Table:-
spt_certification
🔸 Column:-
phase (ya state related field)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔹 CertificationPhase ke Types/stages:-
Common phases 👇

🔸 1. Staged / Created:-
Certification ban gaya hai
Abhi start nahi hua

🔸 2. Active:-
Review chal raha hai
Reviewer kaam kar raha hai

🔸 3. Remediation:-
Revoke wale access remove kiye ja rahe hain

🔸 4. Completed:-
Sab finish ho gaya

🔸 5. Archived:-
Old certification store ho gaya
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔹 CertificationPhase ke andar kya hota hai?
👉 Ye koi heavy object nahi hota,
👉 Mostly ek state/enum type concept hota hai.

🔸 Internally contain karta hai:-
phase name (Active, Completed etc.)
allowed actions
timing (start/end)
transition rules (next phase kya hoga)

🔹 Real Flow samajh le (🔥 important):-
Create Certification
        ↓
Phase = STAGED
        ↓
Start Certification
        ↓
Phase = ACTIVE
        ↓
Reviewer decisions
        ↓
Phase = REMEDIATION
        ↓
Access remove
        ↓
Phase = COMPLETED
-------------------------------------------------------
🔹 Real SailPoint me kya hota hai?
👉 CertificationPhase generally aise hota hai:-
public enum CertificationPhase {
    Staged,
    Active,
    Remediation,
    Completed,
    Archived
}
👉 Matlab:-
Ye sirf values/state define karta hai
Koi heavy getter/setter class nahi hoti.
